{"tid":531420,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[茄子蛋] 有無巴打有聽台灣Band？","createTime":"2018-01-16T20:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T17:37:16.000Z","uid":1863,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"71f2e6a71ec6ba70a23e0d05692c5e28e92cab3c","tid":531420,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T20:32:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x3bDhtuC5yk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx3bDhtuC5yk&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c01ae999\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x3bDhtuC5yk</a><br />\n<br />\n煙一根一根一根的點<br />\n酒一杯一杯一杯的乾<br />\n<br />\n高質MV、高質歌，真心值得欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係MV到最後，你先發現原來兩個後生仔並唔係個阿伯嘅過去，而係存在係同一條時間線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「看三小啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」(望乜撚嘢啊？)<br />\n「看你緣投啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」(望你靚仔啊~)<br />\n<br />\n呢兩句台詞呼應緊嘅正正就係歌名「浪子回頭」，阿伯曾經都MK過，佢開頭望住兩個MK仔笑係因為佢好似望住往日嘅自己、同埋嗰個已逝去嘅朋友(呢個就係佢點解會一路湛酒落隻空杯嘅原因)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/042859_040d7cb0c56131a8fe65c58fcfffe5ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F042859_040d7cb0c56131a8fe65c58fcfffe5ec.png&h=50289b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而佢答句「看你緣投啦～」就係因為佢已經浪子回頭，唔再為小事而同人嘈起上黎，簡單講，亦即係歲月令到佢收咗火，睇到都覺得佬味濃郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/043040_7429ca43191eb1349e3721f4c017dd99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F043040_7429ca43191eb1349e3721f4c017dd99.png&h=64823390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n菸一支一支一支的點 酒一杯一杯一杯的乾<br />\n請你要體諒我 我酒量不好賣給我衝康<br />\n時間一天一天一天的走 汗一滴一滴一滴的流<br />\n有一天 咱都老 帶某子逗陣  浪子回頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/043109_04ec02a43fa3478951e7636fc89f875d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F043109_04ec02a43fa3478951e7636fc89f875d.png&h=b6e411db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇到呢到，你又有無諗起生命中嘅邊一個朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而佢，而家又係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2076474448b54186a9909f667222f69717a37b7b","tid":531420,"uid":1863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T20:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/043357_f46d5ced8812c104fdcb2f1cfffd57a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F043357_f46d5ced8812c104fdcb2f1cfffd57a8.png&h=b490f087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95048e7881286db3f041933ec8ef4a98b66ea76","tid":531420,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T12:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9daa6bd363b9466fd0ab58847de56d21c22f7a","tid":531420,"uid":51325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Y0Ut5ozaKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Y0Ut5ozaKs&d=KQU5AP42oqIWRdNGrjshz26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5b1f53f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Y0Ut5ozaKs</a><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab91c05955a15773cf7ae0f240bb06f1fe9eb1b","tid":531420,"uid":1863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec9daa6bd363b9466fd0ab58847de56d21c22f7a","tid":531420,"uid":51325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:47:20